Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.41,0:02:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya's pressing timings are still not good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.18,0:02:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He is in a hurry to catch up for his lateness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.19,0:02:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's victory or resignation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.32,0:02:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That imperceptible hesitation in your heart \Nis what messes up your timings.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.16,0:02:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to keep by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.89,0:02:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since I was a child, \NI have been constantly hearing that my father is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.77,0:02:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But the truth is, \Nall these 17 years he has simply been missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.74,0:02:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means he very well may still be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.51,0:02:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And if he is still alive, at least once in a lifetime, \NI must find a way to see my real father with my own eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.45,0:02:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.52,0:02:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I am now in Slothium.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.89,0:02:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This very moment, I must fully concentrate \Non the battle right in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.69,0:02:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, I can't move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.07,0:02:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Otonashi is starting to pick up the pace!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.92,0:03:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This is finally getting exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.62,0:03:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Zeroing in. That's the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not enough to turn the tide.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.93,0:03:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't give up the hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.80,0:03:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.80,0:03:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Disengage completely \Nand let your determination do the thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.47,0:03:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fall out of the flow now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.53,0:03:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A continuous bonus!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.18,0:03:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful! Go, go, Ginya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.98,0:04:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Game is concluded. \NWinner - Otonashi Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.89,0:04:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,From game to game, \Nyou are playing hit-and-miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But for now, that's about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition, Mr. Otonashi will be granted an advantage \Nin his next promotion match for the Knight title.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.69,0:04:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.73,0:04:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oumi? Master, you watched it as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Your last minute appearance agitated everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a spectacular clutch. \NJust your thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.67,0:04:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't expect this myself. \NI challenged my luck today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.10,0:04:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We can give you a ride to the cafe. \NHow about it? Wanna celebrate with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.54,0:04:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I'm heading to the Spinning Gears.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.04,0:04:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.46,0:04:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ms. Ishibashi? \NDoing overtime?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.46,0:04:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Already finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.66,0:05:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a reason you come at such hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.70,0:05:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.79,0:05:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... We have our files \Non pachislot designers right about...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.63,0:05:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No. 28 of the previous year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's our Ms. Ishibashi. \NEssentially, a living directory.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.61,0:05:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How rude. \NI'm not that limited you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.18,0:05:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Though to be fair, there are plenty of corporate secrets \Nthat are not to be published. {TODO: Honestly no fucking clue why she said that. Ditto for the next 2 lines.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.72,0:05:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Data of zero value, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.15,0:05:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero value, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly you look for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.89,0:05:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,About 17 years ago, Shinbashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.49,0:05:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it. There's none.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Know anything about that Shinbashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A machine designer, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No longer in active service, I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Designing only attracts young men. \NThose who are older tend to retire to management.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So, wanna get a round? \NOh, right, you're driving a bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.65,0:05:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Later then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,At times she's nice, \Nat times she's ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,In this sunset...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.50,0:06:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I played one day when I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.24,0:06:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.42,0:07:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.49,0:07:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember so little of my whole childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.49,0:07:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Can this photo be the reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.80,0:07:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you awake, Ginya?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.74,0:07:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the second time, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.11,0:07:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That deep sigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your contents' wallet filled? \NYou look ravaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.52,0:07:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ravaged? It's not really that bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.08,0:07:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not amused!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.99,0:07:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to hide from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not hiding a single thing from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.79,0:07:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's so late! \NI gotta work, work!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it was tasty and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.43,0:07:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually he cleans the dish out \Nas though it was just washed...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Something definitely happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He must be going nuts over pachislot again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.84,0:08:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I can feel something weighting his shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.44,0:08:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, you think he is acting weird too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.84,0:08:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.95,0:08:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There's more to it than writing issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.18,0:08:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Something troubles him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.49,0:08:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.02,0:08:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll come in handy. {Опа, подрезал.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.42,0:08:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri's coffee is perfect! \NCan have a refill?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.99,0:08:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.14,0:08:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,For the moment, \Nthis model is number one in demand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The game has become more intense than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.87,0:08:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, the business demands \Nshift with incredible speed, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.44,0:08:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The developers barely manage to catch up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.65,0:08:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.85,0:08:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, does the name \Nof designer Shinbashi ring any bell for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinbashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.16,0:08:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... I can't hear any.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.86,0:08:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How old is this gentleman?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, about 50 or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.56,0:08:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,50 years old designer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:09:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Designing the new models \Nonly attracts young men.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This work is on the leading edge \Nof high-tech after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.27,0:09:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Older ones usually retire to management.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.62,0:09:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If my dad is still alive, even if retired from engineering, \Nhe should still be involved in pachislot business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.80,0:09:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This might help me cheer up a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.34,0:09:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty crowded in here, \Nbut I already fancy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.49,0:09:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He's fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen such a finger wielding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.30,0:10:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,With swift and decisive movements, \Nhe lines up the titles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And still, however swift he is,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.60,0:10:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the firm steadiness \Nis apparent in his movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.07,0:10:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What an amazing sight he constitutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.98,0:10:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He hit it! Even in such places \Nthere are awesome slotters!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.57,0:10:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.35,0:10:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That man's eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.45,0:10:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They are piercing you through.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.42,0:11:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They are not like Daiba's eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.86,0:11:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They are aiming for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.86,0:11:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No... Those are eyes that can stab a man \Nin the most cold-blooded fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.57,0:11:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Those eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The eyes that are used to hating people!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.34,0:11:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? A dustpan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatcha looking at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.75,0:11:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that yours? One should not leave a dustpan \Nin the middle of the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.32,0:11:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,One should walk around it and you're stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.02,0:11:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I recognise this one... \NDo you like boxing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.76,0:11:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I peak hate it, you dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.00,0:11:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That was nowhere near cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.70,0:11:48.67,Song,,0,0,0,,Rising Sun Cafeteria
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.94,0:11:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, \NI haven't eaten since the noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.71,0:11:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to our place...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.11,0:11:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.68,0:11:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.68,0:12:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sup, halfling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.92,0:12:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.98,0:12:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Did this child bring you trouble somehow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.52,0:12:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad to hear then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.43,0:12:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.76,0:12:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Minor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.98,0:12:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira, you can't say such things \Nto our customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.60,0:12:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.74,0:12:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to forgive him. \NSince recently I have to look after that sweet child.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.64,0:12:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You have one busy grandchild.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.41,0:12:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He is not my grandchild, \NI'm just doing a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.71,0:12:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't get me wrong, \Nmy own grandchildren are just as sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.39,0:12:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Please call me when you decide what to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.79,0:12:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what should I try in this ramen house...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.73,0:12:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder at all, \Nit's ginger pork.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.90,0:12:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it ginger pork? \NThen, I'll have pork on rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.94,0:13:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out, hey. \NIt's the ginger pork day. {TODO: Might as well be ginger pork specialized restaurant or a special ginger pork dish etc.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.08,0:13:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,One ginger pork!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.75,0:13:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.76,0:13:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go, bon appetit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Smells great. \NLet's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, so hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.23,0:13:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm hungry here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.00,0:13:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Minor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.10,0:13:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.17,0:13:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Ginya by the way. \NOtonashi Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.64,0:13:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.75,0:13:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool name, right?\NAnd Akira's surname is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.32,0:13:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasamatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.62,0:13:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasamatsu Akira then? \NIt's a good name too. Not as cool as mine though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's times more famed than Ginya's!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.26,0:13:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasamatsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.33,0:13:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Some talented singer I reckon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.40,0:13:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.96,0:13:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What? He's famed, right? That'll do!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.84,0:14:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.41,0:14:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, dad, did you win?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.61,0:14:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.85,0:14:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that man again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.99,0:14:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The clingy one is Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.89,0:14:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Otonashi Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.33,0:14:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to apologize for earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.69,0:14:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasamatsu. \NYou have to excuse my son's coarseness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.56,0:14:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget to take a bath! \NWe'll see you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.08,0:14:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was that man's child.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.18,0:14:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you acquainted to Mr. Kasamatsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.98,0:14:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Seen him in a parlor once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira's face... \Nis shining whenever he sees his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.69,0:14:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a papa's boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.39,0:15:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He misses his mother a lot \Nthough she's long gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you really blame him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.83,0:15:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't have a mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If I knew more, I'd tell more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.33,0:15:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomiko! We need your help with the washing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.54,0:15:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just gossiping with this young chap here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How much I owe?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.74,0:15:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be 680 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.88,0:15:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see. Six hundred and eighty yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.09,0:15:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It is that man again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.39,0:15:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a boxing champion once?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.36,0:15:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,As a junior lightweight, \Nhe had a comparatively successful career.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.80,0:15:47.74,Song,,0,0,0,,Kasamatsu Ryu (Tsutsumi Gym) \NA signature Razor Jab!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.74,0:15:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasamatsu... Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsutsumi Gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.32,0:16:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I was I child once too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.22,0:16:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Although not quite as cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.84,0:16:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back! This is mine! \NYou have to return it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.67,0:16:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.62,0:16:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,As a product of the lonely childhood myself, \Nsomehow I can tell we are similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.56,0:16:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You like boxing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.68,0:16:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate it the most, dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.05,0:16:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.65,0:16:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He is so much like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.99,0:16:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't do at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.95,0:17:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kasamatsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.76,0:17:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Has he not retired from boxing long ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.33,0:17:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.19,0:17:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind if I sit next to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.23,0:17:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so keen about it, \Nyou start as soon as the parlor is open.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.33,0:17:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kasamatsu, \Nyou were an incredible boxer, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all long past now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.51,0:18:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. And that speed. \NIt's like a Razor Jab reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.61,0:18:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,With precise, steady movements and a shrewd eye, \Nyou deliver a punch full of pure instinct to your enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.99,0:18:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Capture the rhythm of your opponent \Nand then impose your own pace upon him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.81,0:18:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This can easily be applied \Nto catching the machine's rhythm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.70,0:18:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive technique only worthy of a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.07,0:18:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you looking for a fight with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Fighting you is clearly a suicide for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.04,0:18:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I'm also keen about pachislot, \Nand would like to learn from you, Mr. Kasamatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.48,0:18:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to challenge me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.79,0:18:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever hits more in 10 minutes, wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.42,0:18:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.94,0:18:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I win, you shut that mouth of yours \Nand get it as far away from me as feasible. Deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds fair to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.20,0:18:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.54,0:19:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Did this man \Nnever forget a thing from his boxing youth?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.44,0:19:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He is still training as a practicing boxer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.91,0:19:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard it helps them \Nmaintain the body even afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.05,0:19:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.60,0:19:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.02,0:19:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kasamatsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.52,0:19:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't actually have \Nany regrets about boxing, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.64,0:19:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.56,0:20:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what Akira said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.36,0:20:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,"I hate boxing more than anything."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.43,0:20:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,However children tend to say things \Nwhich are opposite to how they really feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,"Love" will be "Hate" in Childish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.04,0:20:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of your snooping!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just trying to feed my son Akira! \NThat's why I'm playing pachislot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.71,0:20:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my life, and mine only!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.85,0:20:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what you're getting next time! \NI'll mess you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.47,0:20:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.07,0:20:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you have a dream in that little chest of yours. \NAnd I understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.91,0:20:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You have every reason to call me a dumbass \Nfor being that unduly nosy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.54,0:20:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But I saw how your face changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.15,0:20:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready to go to the extremes \Nin all of your undertakings?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.34,0:21:20.69,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}The heavy rain is over now, \NShadows have ceased to roam, \NEven summer itself has come to an end
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.34,0:21:20.71,Song,,0,0,5,,Ame wa yande ita kage to aruide ita natsu ga owatte ita
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.69,0:21:34.27,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}My youth goes on, pushing me in my back with no rest,\NAnd the scarlet sky will soon start pouring water again
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:34.29,Song,,0,0,5,,Seishun ga boku no senaka o oshite akai sora utsuru mizutamari
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.27,0:21:47.89,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}With my leg in a clutch, suddenly the sky shivered, \NSo unawares, making such stupid look!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.29,0:21:47.89,Song,,0,0,5,,Ashimoto ga tora rete ite sora wa ureru bakaridatta
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.89,0:21:54.56,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}So it will remain forever,\NAs I will remain forever so!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.89,0:21:54.56,Song,,0,0,5,,Konomama de īkai boku wa konomama de īkai
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.56,0:22:01.63,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}So do we, the way we are now, \NWe surely will remain forever too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.56,0:22:01.63,Song,,0,0,5,,Kimi to konomama zutto konomama de īkai
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.63,0:22:08.21,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}So it will remain forever,\NAs I will remain forever so!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.63,0:22:08.22,Song,,0,0,5,,Konomama de īkai boku wa konomama de īkai
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.21,0:22:15.68,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2\fade(0,800)}So do we, the way we are now, \NWe surely will remain forever too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.22,0:22:15.68,Song,,0,0,5,,{\fade(0,800)}Kimi to konomama zutto konomama de īkai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.93,0:22:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweet child.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.75,0:22:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Setback.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.71,0:22:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Road to the champ.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.08,0:22:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.39,0:22:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasamatsu's hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.89,0:22:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.72,0:22:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time: \NFather and Son.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.49,0:22:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,My finger will\Nstop the time.
